Ridin’ on a horse, ha🐴🤠 u can whip your Porsche ;)

🎤🎶Explained by Lil Nas X himself, Old Town Road represents the path to success, wealth, fortune, and all that good stuff he’s experiencing. Lil Nas X believes his opportunities are limitless, hence why he’s going to ride till he can’t no more. “I got the horses in the back” represents how Lil Nas X is traveling on his journey to success and his acknowledgement of the talent he has to give to the world. 

The lyrics “Ridin’ on a horse, ha / You can whip your Porsche” are meant to show he knows he has the talent and doesn’t need anything special or complicated to make it ✨🙏🤍 

Article by @cosmopolitan https://www.cosmopolitan.com/entertainment/music/a28497104/old-town-road-lyrics-meaning-lil-nas-x-billy-ray-cyrus/
